Hands-on experience with unit testing and TDD.<br />\r\n•\tAny experience of SVN, Github and NuGet (but not essential). <br />\r\n<br />\r\nSkills Required<br />\r\nPHP , C#/.NET, HTML/DHTML, JavaScript, SalesForce, ruby-on-rails, python, node.js, ruby, java.  <br />\r\n<br />\r\nGeneral Requirements<br />\r\n•\tExcellent written and verbal English communication skills.<br />\r\n•\tA strong team player with good interpersonal skills and willingness to contribute.<br />\r\n•\tShould be self-disciplined, pro-active, self-motivated and responsible.<br />\r\n•\tAble to work independently with minimum supervision.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBenefits include<br />\r\n•\tCompetitive salary with 6 monthly performance/bonus reviews.<br />\r\n•\tWork with an inspiring team, learn from the best talent on the planet.<br />\r\n•\tPotential to grow into a Team Leader, build and run your own team within our company.<br />\r\n•\tWork from home, 100% teleworking.<br />\r\n•\tLong term engagement, which should last many years for the right candidate.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you are interested in this position, please send your CV specifying your salary expectations in USD dollars for a full-time position per month to this e-mail: hr@groupdocs.com", :feed_id => 2)
